data.description: This 2022 construction beauty boasts 2100 sqft of modern elegance. 4 spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths & ample storage. Step into a bright & airy interior with tall ceilings, white blinds, & farmhouse style doors for that perfect touch of charm. The heart of the home is the stunning white kitchen featuring granite countertops, pantry, extended cabinets, large island, & SS appliances. Enjoy the luxury of upgraded bathroom tiles, adding a touch of sophistication to your daily routine. With NO HOA, you have the freedom to make this home uniquely yours. All bedrooms have ethernet drops for added speed. The large covered back patio is an ideal spot for entertaining, overlooking the expansive fenced backyard with automatic sprinkler system where endless possibilities await. The owner's retreat is a true haven with double vanities, garden tub, huge shower, & a walk-in closet designed for your wardrobe dreams. Epoxied garage floors make for easy clean up. Convenient location to shops & highway!
